Conference Service  Center will  help you  by reserving  a car  to serve
you.

SOCIAL PROGRAM
  A  special  social  program  will  aquaint  participants with the most
interesting places in Moscow and  nearby cities.  Main tours  are listed
in  the  Participant  Registration  Form.   Additional  tours  will   be
available during the Conference.
  The first tour  of Moscow is  free for the  registered participants of
the Conference.
  Each evening a  special bus will  take participants to  Moscow popular
restaurants and  places of  interest and  after 3  hours repeat  the way
back to take the Conference participants to the hotel.

